Class TripInformation.TravelTime

    TripInformation

    public static class TripInformation.TravelTime
extends java.lang.Object
    Travel Time class represents a prediction of a travel time in a particular route starting at a particular departure time or ending at a particular arrival time. This class specifies the travel time for that departure time or arrival time it also has other information such as road closures, restrictions, average speed and any abnormality travel time in minutes.
